# wargame_rl

Reinforcement learning project that trains agents (DQN, PPO) to play tabletop wargames on a discrete grid. Agents control multiple models (units) using polar-coordinate movement to capture objectives.

**Stack**: Python 3.12+ ¬∑ UV ¬∑ Gymnasium 1.x ¬∑ PyTorch + Lightning ¬∑ Wandb ¬∑ Pydantic + pydantic-yaml ¬∑ Typer ¬∑ Loguru ¬∑ Pygame
**Tooling**: Just ¬∑ Ruff (fmt/lint, 88 cols) ¬∑ Mypy (strict) ¬∑ isort ¬∑ autoflake ¬∑ Pytest ¬∑ Pre-commit

- **Python 3.13** (UV package manager, `uv.lock`)
- **Gymnasium 1.x** ‚Äî RL environment (`WargameEnv`)
- **PyTorch + PyTorch Lightning** ‚Äî DQN and PPO training
- **Wandb** ‚Äî experiment tracking & video recording
- **Pydantic + pydantic-yaml** ‚Äî config & type models
- **Typer** ‚Äî CLI (`train.py`, `simulate.py`)
- **Loguru** ‚Äî logging
- **Pygame** ‚Äî human rendering

## Development Tooling

- **Just** ‚Äî command runner (see `Justfile`)
- **Ruff** ‚Äî linter & formatter (line length 88, double quotes)
- **Mypy** ‚Äî strict type checking (`disallow_untyped_defs`, `no_implicit_optional`)
- **isort** ‚Äî import sorting (Black profile)
- **autoflake** ‚Äî removes unused imports
- **Pytest** ‚Äî testing
- **Pre-commit** ‚Äî hooks for all of the above

## Key Commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Setup | `just setup` |
| Sync deps | `just dev-sync` |
| Format | `just format` |
| Lint | `just lint` |
| Test | `just test` |
| Full validation | `just validate` |
| Train (PPO, default) | `just train <config.yaml>` |
| Train (DQN) | `just train <config.yaml> dqn` |
| Train multiple configs in parallel | `just train-multi config1.yaml config2.yaml` |
| Simulate | `just simulate-latest` |

## Project Layout

- `wargame_rl/wargame/envs/` ‚Äî Gymnasium environment, reward (phases, calculators e.g. closest_objective, group_cohesion, vp_gain; success criteria e.g. all_at_objectives, player_vp_min ‚Äî see [docs/reward-phases.md](docs/reward-phases.md)), rendering, types (see [docs/ddd-envs.md](docs/ddd-envs.md) for DDD structure and extension)
- `wargame_rl/wargame/model/dqn/` ‚Äî DQN agent, Lightning module, replay buffer, config
- `wargame_rl/wargame/model/ppo/` ‚Äî PPO actor-critic, Lightning module, agent, config
- `wargame_rl/wargame/model/common/` ‚Äî Shared: factory, observation, dataset, device, wandb, callbacks
- `wargame_rl/wargame/model/net.py` ‚Äî RL_Network base, MLPNetwork, TransformerNetwork
- `wargame_rl/wargame/types.py` ‚Äî `Experience` / `ExperienceBatch`
- `examples/env_config/` ‚Äî YAML env configs
- `tests/` ‚Äî Pytest suite, fixtures in `conftest.py`
- `docs/` ‚Äî design docs (DDD in envs: `docs/ddd-envs.md`)
- `train.py` / `simulate.py` / `main.py` ‚Äî entry points
